{"tid":2256181,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《鬼滅之刃》現像 ，小朋友冷靜打針 ，「全集中的呼吸哦！」醫療現場護士大派用場","createTime":"2020-10-24T07:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T11:56:16.000Z","uid":54930,"like":30,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0416806bc98501147d7caec91e2291afeef7a936","tid":2256181,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:04:52.000Z","msg":"【#LikeJapan遊戲動漫】大熱動畫《鬼滅之刃》不但成為了社會現象，還能在醫療現場幫上大忙？！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/myf4BaH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmyf4BaH.png&h=5a965f8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有護士在Twitter上分享，表示替孩子們抽血、打針或處理傷口等情況時只要跟他們說：「全集中的呼吸哦！！！」對方便馬上明白要深呼吸、冷靜下來，幫了個大忙呢！<br />\n雖然也不是每一個孩子也能用到這個方法，但那位護士提及最近使用率提升了，而且還挺見效的。<br />\n<br />\n除了護士外，有藥劑師及放射治療師等醫護人員也表示利用《鬼滅之刃》的「招式」成功哄到不少孩子冷靜下來、還會乖乖吃藥！看來《鬼滅之刃》的影響力真的很厲害啊⋯⋯！<br />\n<br />\n原帖：<a href=\"http://twitter.com/i/events/1317358917333045249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fi%2Fevents%2F1317358917333045249&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=d43ac93a\" target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/i/events/1317358917333045249</a><br />\nby #LikeJapan_hoki<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/likejpn/photos/a.366319040144677/3196698700440016/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flikejpn%2Fphotos%2Fa.366319040144677%2F3196698700440016%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=037e1c36\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/likejpn/photos/a.366319040144677/3196698700440016/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"1ebd0629e7750f351f75936647f07e6839c39432","tid":2256181,"uid":314983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"